<paragraph blockId="34.[189,1398,990,1052]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Dedicated to Claire Villemant, MNHN curator, hymenopterologist and ichneumonomaniac, adviser, teacher, supporter, coach and friend.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
